  <additions>
<list>
<item xml:id="a1">
<locus target="#273r"/>
<desc>A note stating that this volume was written by the order of king <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10375Yohanne">John I</persName> for himself and his children when Sinodā was ʾabuna.
To the names of John and <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS8278SablaWa">Sabla Wangel</persName> subsequently has been subsequently added that of their daughter <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13245WalattaRufael">Walatta
Rufāʾel</persName>.</desc>
<q xml:lang="gez"><seg part="I">ነዋ፡ አዘዝነ፡ ንሕነ፡ አእላፍ፡ ሰገድ፡ ወበጸጋ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ዘተሰመይነ፡ ዮሐንስሃ፡ ያውግዙ፡ እንበይነ፡ ዛቲ፡ መጽሐፍነ፡ ዘአጽሐፍናሃ፡ ንሕነ፡
በዘመነ፡ መንግሥትነ፡ ለበቍዔተ፡ ነፍስነ። ከመ፡ ኢያውፅኣ፡ እምቤተ፡ ውሉድነ፡ ዘወለድናሆሙ፡ በሥጋ። መኑሂ፡ እምሰብእ፡ እመሂ፡ ንጉሥ፡ ወእመሂ፡ መኰንን።</seg></q>
</item>

<item xml:id="a2">
<desc>At the beginning of each month, at the foot of the page, is a name, probably that of a scribe.</desc>
<q xml:lang="gez">ዘ<persName role="scribe" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13257TawaldaMadhen">ተወልደ፡ መድኅን፡</persName> ዘ<persName role="scribe" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13258ZamanfasQeddus">ዘመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡</persName>,
ዘ<persName role="scribe" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13259TaklaMaryam">ተክለ፡ ማርያም፡</persName>, ዘ<persName role="scribe" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13260Asaf">አሳፍ፡</persName>,
ዘ<persName role="scribe" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13261Giyorgis">ጊዮርጊስ፡</persName>, ዘ<persName role="scribe" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13262DamaKrestos">ደመ፡ ክርስቶስ።</persName></q>
</item>

<item xml:id="a3">
    <locus target="#1r"/>
    <desc type="OwnershipNote">The note states that the manuscript belongs to the church of <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/INS0101MadhaneAlam">Madḫāne ʿAlam</placeName>
    </desc>
    <q xml:lang="gez">ስንክሳር፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ መድኃኔ ፡ ዓለም።</q>

</item>

</list>
